            "title": "穩定幣相關股午後飛升   金管局將公布穩定幣發行人選",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">市場炒賣穩定幣發牌股，證券股大幅炒上，銀行股造好。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">金管局今日下午5時舉行穩定幣發行人技術簡報會，隨後持牌穩定幣發行人將會見傳媒。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"Shutterstock圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/12/20231228_FI_source_licensed_穩定幣3_shutterstock_704.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"Shutterstock圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/12/20231228_FI_source_licensed_穩定幣3_shutterstock_704.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">Shutterstock圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">傳聞獲發牌的虛擬資產交易VATP平台OSL(00863）升3.48%，報14.58元 ; 滙豐控股(00005)升0.9%，報140.2元 ; 渣打集團(02888)升1.68%，報181.7元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">國泰君安國際(01788)最高見3.59元，升48.35%，現升30.99%，報3.17元，成交38.8億元 ; 雲鋒金融(00376)升9.79%，報3.14元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">耀才證券金融(01428)升4.14%，報12.58元 ; 招商證券(06099)升4.67%，報13.91元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">另一持牌虛擬資產交易平台HASHKEY(03887) 揚8.72%，報4.99元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15856450-%e7%a9%a9%e5%ae%9a%e5%b9%a3%e7%9b%b8%e9%97%9c%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e9%a3%9b%e5%8d%87-%e9%87%91%e7%ae%a1%e5%b1%80%e5%85%ac%e5%b8%83%e7%a9%a9%e5%ae%9a%e5%b9%a3%e7%99%bc%e8%a1%8c%e4%ba%ba",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/20231228_FI_source_licensed_stable-coin_shutterstock_704.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-10 14:21:30",
