        },
        {
            "title": "阿里巴巴HappyHorse正內部測試   傳4月30日開放",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內地傳媒報道，阿里巴巴(09988)ATH(Alibaba Token Hub)表示，HappyHorse是阿里ATH旗下創新事業部研發的模型，正處於內測中，將於近期開放API。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20260129_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20260129_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">報道稱，ATH創新事業部已啟動AI時代的全新交互方式探索計劃，HappyHorse是這個探索方向的一部分，更多的產品會陸續推出。另有報道指，HappyHorse開放API訪問功能的時間為4月30日。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">ATH(Alibaba Token Hub)是阿里於3月16日成立，由阿里首席執行官吳泳銘領導，整合通義實驗室、MaaS業務線、千問事業部、悟空事業部及AI創新事業部五大部份。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15856412-%e9%98%bf%e9%87%8c%e5%b7%b4%e5%b7%b4happyhorse%e6%ad%a3%e5%85%a7%e9%83%a8%e6%b8%ac%e8%a9%a6-%e5%82%b34%e6%9c%8830%e6%97%a5%e9%96%8b%e6%94%be",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260323_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-10 14:11:18",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
